There has been a lot of reaction from social media as a member of DSS (Department of State service) personnel reportedly shot a Nigerian Army personnel for no tangible reasons.
The decease who was identified as Peter who is recognized as a Nigerian Army was murdered days after he was shot by a DSS personnel in the Lekki area of Lagos State.
According to Sahara reporters, Peter was interrogated by DSS operatives and he made an attempt of bringing out his ID card to prove that he belongs to the Nigerian Army, and that was the action that claims his life.
After this incident took place, the family of The decease (Peter) has been seeking justice on behalf of their murdered son.

